    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it really is. i feel like a shell. like i'm just walking around a house that isn't even mine anymore. i try to tell myself things will get better eventually, but i don't believe it. i don't think it's possible to feel whole again when half of me is gone. is there even a point to trying to fix something that's just... permanently broken?",
